  "title": "Project Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p><ul><li>Annual Performance Appraisal</li><li>Career Progression</li><li>Comprehensive Medical Insurance</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Engineering, Construction, or related fields.</li><li>Strong communication and written skills for both English and Mandarin</li><li>Minimum 4 years of Aluminium Glazing and Facade Experience</li></ul><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Coordinate daily project activities and ensure timely completion</li><li>Prepare project schedules, reports and technical documents</li><li>Supervise site activities and ensure safety compliance</li><li>Attend site meetings and liaise with clients/contractors/suppliers</li><li>Solve site issues and ensure work quality meets specifications</li><li>Handle manpower arrangement, material delivery coordination and installation progress</li><li>Maintain proper documentation for drawings, reports and submissions</li></ul>",
